metadata.name: CKF NFT
metadata.description:
The Galley is releasing their first NFT collection in line with their new CKF Cannabis Rosin product lines.  The Purchaser of this NFTs will have the rights to a MYTHC coupon that allows them one free product delivered once the purchaser has confirmed they are 21+ and live within the California where a state licensed cannabis delivery company will deliver to state qualified customers of legal age and legal address.

After minting your NFT, we will provide a landing page for you to share you email to receive your MYTCH coupon that will unlock your free product
